      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Warm up the <strong>gravy</strong> over a low heat</p><p>Slice the<strong> rested turkey </strong>finely on a clean board</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced turkey</strong> with the<strong> pigs in blankets</strong>,<strong> stuffing meatballs</strong>, <strong>rosemary roast potatoes</strong>, <strong>honey roast veg</strong> and <strong>roasted sprouts</strong></p><p>Add a dollop of <strong>cranberry sauce</strong> to the side and drizzle over the <strong>gravy</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
